> What did you use for a gasket?
>
> Felpro Hi-temp Gasket material.


Probably could use anything. I had an 80's Chevy Spectrum (Isuzu I-Mark)
that blew the EGR valve. I capped the exhaust riser tube with a rubber cap.
Worked fine. Tom's right: Without the exhaust actually passing through it,
there's little heat to worry about.

